metadata.name: JAC FOR THRIVE
metadata.description:
It's Jac's yearly fundraiser for Thrive! 

Just 0.01 ETH feeds a child for 1 month!

Food is the most basic need for survival.  Still, 1 in 10 of the world’s population is hungry.

Thrive fills the nutrition gap. The children Thrive supports face significant micronutrient deficiencies that can lead to delayed brain and muscle development. The meals provide 50% of a child’s daily nutritional needs.
